The paper discusses the use of deep networks for learning models on mobile devices, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and distributed computing (cs.DC). Given that the paper focuses on the practical method for federated learning of deep networks, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG), followed by artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and distributed computing (cs.DC).
